ABAP - Advanced Business Application Programming
High-Level Language
Need a basis of Java and SQL

3-Tier Architecture
  - Database      - RDBMS
  - Application   - ABAP
  - Presentation  - SAP GUI
  
System Distribution
  - Development System
  - Testing System
  - Production System
Transport system to transfer data and transactions into the next tier

Types of Programs
  - Reports
  - Dynpros

Work Processes
  - Dispatcher
      Controls the distribution of work process to system users
  - Dynpro Processer
      Handle dialogue control, only on the flowing logic not data process
  - ABAP Processer
      Receive information from dialogue and process data
  - Database Interface
      Database inpendent ABAP transactions that ensures all codes works right
